{"type": "article", "id": 40697, "title": "日本书店推出一款泡面，据说可以“补脑”", "description": "如果嗜好收集奇奇怪怪的事物，不妨去这家书店一看", "date": "2017-05-13T23:15:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 1865, "name": "书店"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 45, "praise_count": 331, "image": "img/article/article_show/201705111619445sQRNA64KlzCcYO3.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">“方便面”的发源地日本最近又推出一款“脑面”（脳麺），最大的噱头在于补脑。</p><p class=\"\">来看一眼“脳麺”的包装设计，宣传海报也用了大脑的元素，连面饼都是脑浆粉色。据说面饼中添加了补脑的维生素 B1，售价 400 日元。</p><p class=\"\">呃，我们觉得补脑的效果也就那样，这款包装清奇的泡面更多还是活跃在社交网络的自拍里，根据网友的反馈，“脑浆”调味包的味道还蛮咸的……</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170512142050egf7yk0pQRqAOztT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170512142108Rb1LtMqT2woPQalG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705121421225fCao2veDUk6YmRE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">这款泡面的生产商并非传统速食面制造商，而是日本书店 VILLAGE VANGUARD 与扭蛋制造商 Takara Tommy 旗下的“熊猫之穴”系列推出的联名商品。VILLAGE VANGUARD 在日本拥有 500 多家门店，与其说是一家连锁书店，倒更像是一间嬉皮另类、贩卖生活方式的杂货店。</p><p class=\"\">除了书籍，VILLAGE VANGUARD 还售卖热门 CD、潮流义务、零售、玩具……从幼儿到老年人的商品都有，消费群体很广泛，也有不少游客会慕名前来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170512144020YCHcNEVPqJpTyvXR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017051214402958fohetZpr4VCRSN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170512144040IyG2kcdE6zRWP9A7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.717391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">在“脳麺”之前，这两家品牌还推出过一款联名商品“说谎 T 恤（ウソT）”，在社交网络上得到不少好评。</p><p class=\"\">明明是一杯冰汽水，T恤上却印着“好烫！”?<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170512150056g4nrqO5KwvUs6ID0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">图片是米饭，文字却写着面包?</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170512150152vSMfcrulULyYJep9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">为了挖掘更多有意思的物品，VILLAGE VANGUARD 还会定期举办趣味杂货大赏，<a href=\"https://reg18.smp.ne.jp/regist/is?SMPFORM=lfkc-njsal-996e42796b22d0fee4c7ccc9288f0072\" rel=\"nofollow\">把消费者普遍喜爱的商品罗列出来，让网友们进行投票</a>。</p><p class=\"\">比如下面这把自带出场 BGM 效果的“漫画伞”、帮助你脱非入欧的“氪金运+++招运符”，都是你在这家日本书店能买到的脑洞好物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170512182454TPYmVvcaI3BpwOik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.425000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170512182641JI4RUMrqzLQ8wtE2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.567187\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：VILLAGE VANGUARD</p>"}